{"tid":709752,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"bc shop 兼職真係笨柒先做","createTime":"2018-06-20T09:09:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T12:28:27.000Z","uid":188301,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1dd61ceb2abcf3529c2930fdf135cb22e8f58378","tid":709752,"uid":188301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:09:36.000Z","msg":"有健身既都一定知道bc shop<br />\n我今日就去左見工 (part time)<br />\n咁一開始條友就講兼職全職都一樣要training<br />\n仲話要train一個月 咁期間就50$/hr <br />\n講撚到一定要教到啲員工識晒啲產品 話成千鳩幾樣野<br />\n之後話如果training期間 突然唔做走人的話<br />\n公司係會收番training 期間你返工賺既所有錢<br />\n聽到呢到已經覺得好撚戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後再話 過左training 就要試用期三個月 期間55$/hr<br />\n我心諗兼職都要搞三個月試用？真係好鳩<br />\n之後話期間你唔做/公司炒你<br />\n都係有權收番晒所有人工<br />\n嘩屌咁你炒鳩我 我咪幫你白做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後話冇得你揀返邊間分店 公司根據你能力調派<br />\n話例如：一星期你可能返3日工<br />\n咁呢3日都有機會去唔同既分店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嘩屌那星 人工已經唔係高 仲要懶係野咁多要求<br />\n之後我問朋友 佢地話 收番人工係犯法<br />\n咁我就唔識了 總之呢份兼職真係搵笨柒做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2e4bf93b7c2592ab069e9e233bb68854fd7fe3","tid":709752,"uid":78971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:14:36.000Z","msg":"之後話期間你唔做/公司炒你<br />\n都係有權收番晒所有人工<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁撚on9都講得出"},{"pid":"ed23ad93da81cc3bfe552974ac18e2feae45f2ea","tid":709752,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:16:04.000Z","msg":"可以搵勞工處了"},{"pid":"f4a468ee23a537a6d3774ee87e97216e73d02e43","tid":709752,"uid":188301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af2e4bf93b7